## Limitations

- <%=vars.product_short%> does not support scaling down of the cluster.
- <%=vars.product_short%> does not support plan migrations.
The `-p` option to the `cf update-service` command is not supported.
- <%=vars.product_short%> does not publish locator metrics for service
instances created as Co-located Single VM plans or Co-located Multi VM plans.
- The <%=vars.component_product%> Developer REST API is not available for data operations.
